description: PRODUCT OVERVIEWThe OnePlus Nord N30 packs a powerful punch, combining premium specs and the power of 5G at an entry-level price. A premium 6.72” 120Hz display keeps all your content smooth & fluid. Powered by a massive 5000mAh battery & 50W SUPERVOOC Charging, the Nord N30 5G handles all your favorite content & apps without breaking a sweat. With 128GB of storage (expandable up to 1TB), you’ll have all the space you need to store your photos, videos, and favorite content. Upgrade your smartphone experience with the OnePlus Nord N30 5G today. KEY FEATURES5G speed - Unleash the power & connectivity of 5G. Download or stream your favorite content without waiting on slow network speeds. *5G available in select areas; please check with your carrier.Premium display - The Nord N30 5G features a 6.72” display with an adaptive 120Hz refresh rate, delivering a more fluid viewing experience in day-to-day use.Qualcomm Snapdragon 695 - The powerful Qualcomm Snapdragon 695 5G chipset has improved power efficiency, so you can game, stream, or use your favorite apps for even longer. Powered with 8GB of RAM, you’ll have all the power you need in the palm of your hand.Large battery - A large 5000mAh battery keeps you powered through your day & helps you stay unplugged longer.Ultra-fast charging - The N30 5G comes with a 50W SUPERVOOC Charger included in the box! Spend less time connected to your charger and more time immersed in your phone.Expandable storage - The N30 5G comes with 128GB of internal storage, expandable up to 1TB via MicroSD Card.Fast & smooth software - Experience the iconic Fast & Smooth user interface of OnePlus phones with OxygenOS, based on Android 13.Secure & safe - Keep your device secure with the side-mounted fingerprint sensor or the face unlock feature.Dual stereo speakers - Enjoy your music, podcasts, & other audio with powerful Dual Stereo Speakers, with 200% Ultra Volume Mode.
